{
  "title": "Cohabitation and marriage in Austria",
  "abstract": "Although cohabitation has spread rapidly in Austria during the past decades, it is more a prelude than an alternative to marriage. The individualization thesis serves as a conceptual framework for explaining the rise of cohabiting unions.",
